Reasoning: The talk focuses on statistical viewpoints in the context of massive datasets, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and statistics (cs.ST). The talk also mentions the breakdown of classical viewpoints when data size becomes large, which is a common problem in data science (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the talk may touch on information theory (cs.IT) as it relates to the formulation of big data experiments.
